[confidence-redirect/verify Stage-0 — data-gen pipeline, 2026-06-20]

# Intent / north-star
Train a model that self-emits a STUDENT-calibrated confidence and DECIDES
redirect (low-conf / confidently-wrong) vs verify (high-conf, checkable) vs none.
Useful metacognition -> accuracy, useful ONLY. Calibration is a sub-signal.

