# Decision (user-delegated): VERIFY-LED full build. redirect is CAUSALLY rare (3x confirmed:
# PG0 + decorative-split + control-recovers). Build the ~250 genuine redirects + ~1251 verifies,
# NO padding (padding = v8 hollow-redirect that RL cut, v1=0.651 < baseline 0.786). DCPO triobj RL
# (R_corr + R_meta(PMI) + R_cal) then selects whichever metacognition raises accuracy.

# Infra incident: full local teacher build OOM-killed at 117GB RSS (dump is only 12MB).
# Root cause = NOT the TRAPI API: _check_correctness fed the WHOLE teacher essay (<=4000 tok) to
# math_verify(parsing_timeout=None, disabled for thread-safety); a control sample's pathological
# expression (huge nested exponent/factorial) made sympy allocate unboundedly + the global sympy
# cache compounded over ~1.6e4 grades.
# Fix = _grade_answer parses ONLY the extracted short final answer (last \boxed / 'answer is X');
# long/pathological candidates skip sympy. SYMPY_USE_CACHE=no + clear_cache() per chunk +
# chunked/resumable build (CHUNK_SIZE=250, max_workers=6). Pathological-essay test: <1s, correct.
# After fix: build RSS flat at 0.36GB (was climbing past several GB by this elapsed time pre-fix).

# Tests: 41 (build + grade-safety + sft redirect-mask + concurrency-equivalence) green.
